<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١٠⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5361">مَالِكِ بْنِ أَنَسٍ </a>، عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4473">الْعَلَاءِ بْنِ عَبْدِ الرَّحْمَنِ </a>أَنَّهُ سَمِعَ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3668">أَبَا السَّائِبِ مَوْلَى هِشَامِ بْنِ زُهْرَةَ </a>يَقُولُ: سَمِعْتُ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3320">أَبَا هُرَيْرَةَ </a>يَقُولُ: قَالَ رَسُولُ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> <span class="c2">(ح)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>